ium/top-idf-officer-to-be-questioned-after-calls-for-leaders-to-be-worthy-of-their-soldiers/0000018e-390b-d2fd-a1fe-3dfbe9980000</guid></item><item><title>戏剧性的转变，以色列表示打算向加沙“淹没”人道主义援助</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-13/ty-article/.premium/israel-changes-its-policy-on-supplies-to-gaza-intends-to-flood-in-aid-idf-says/0000018e-390e-db12-a9ef-fbff14c50000</link><description>这一决定是在国际社会向内塔尼亚胡政府施加巨大压力之后做出的，包括在华盛顿和伦敦对来访的部长本尼·甘茨提出严厉警告，甘茨被告知以色列需要采取更多措施来缓解加沙地带的饥饿</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 18:42:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-13/ty-article/.premium/israel-changes-its-policy-on-supplies-to-gaza-intends-to-flood-in-aid-idf-says/0000018e-390e-db12-a9ef-fbff14c50000</guid></item><item><title>战争中的以色列：您需要了解的信息 – 第 159 天</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-03-13/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-what-you-need-to-know-day-159/0000018e-38e1-d21d-a3ef-3be787fe0000</link><description>南非表示，持有南非公民身份的以色列国防军士兵在进入该国时将被逮捕 ■ 在与拜登之间前所未有的紧张局势中，内塔尼亚胡预计将在参议院共和党撤退问题上发表讲话 ■ 近东救济工程处：据报道，以色列袭击拉法食品配送中心后，至少一名工作人员被杀 ■ 这是自以来的首次10 月 7 日，运载援助物资的卡车直接从以色列进入加沙北部 ■ 战争开始 159 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 17:39:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-03-13/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-what-you-need-to-know-day-159/0000018e-38e1-d21d-a3ef-3be787fe0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列一直将约旦河西岸与加沙地带分开。战争期间就等于死刑</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-03-13/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israel-has-been-separating-the-west-bank-from-gaza-during-war-it-becomes-a-death-sentence/0000018e-3874-d2fd-a1fe-3df58c940000</link><description>自上世纪90年代以来，以色列一直致力于将巴勒斯坦领土分为两部分。事实上，加沙人暂时流离失所到西岸并未被考虑，这表明以色列造成的分裂是多么根深蒂固。</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 17:23:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-03-13/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israel-has-been-separating-the-west-bank-from-gaza-during-war-it-becomes-a-death-sentence/0000018e-3874-d2fd-a1fe-3df58c940000</guid></item><item><title>以色列议会批准以色列修订后的2024年预算，为加沙战争提供资金，解决联盟争端</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-13/ty-article/.premium/knesset-approves-israels-amended-2024-budget-to-fund-gaza-war-amid-coalition-dispute/0000018e-3863-dda5-a9ff-fdefb3cc0000</link><description>在与战争无关的支出问题上出现政治争端和分歧后，2024 年修订预算法以 62 名支持者对 55 名反对者的多数票获得通过</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 16:22:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-13/ty-article/.premium/knesset-approves-israels-amended-2024-budget-to-fund-gaza-war-amid-coalition-dispute/0000018e-3863-dda5-a9ff-fdefb3cc0000</guid></item><item><title>与甘茨分手后，萨尔可能获得战时内阁席位——但内塔尼亚胡担心本-格维尔的要求也会随之而来</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-13/ty-article/.premium/saar-could-get-a-war-cabinet-seat-but-netanyahu-fears-ben-gvirs-demands-will-follow/0000018e-3801-d21d-a3ef-3b4721070000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡并不急于屈服于萨尔的要求，而甘茨的人民坚持认为战时内阁中唯一的空闲席位是为亚伊尔·拉皮德保留的</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 15:03:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-13/ty-article/.premium/saar-could-get-a-war-cabinet-seat-but-netanyahu-fears-ben-gvirs-demands-will-follow/0000018e-3801-d21d-a3ef-3b4721070000</guid></item><item><title>病毒式斋月广告聚焦以色列加沙战争中的巴勒斯坦儿童</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-03-13/ty-article/.premium/the-viral-ramadan-commercial-spotlighting-palestinian-children-amid-israels-war-in-gaza/0000018e-3389-d9f7-a5ee-f7cbd44a0000</link><description>科威特电信巨头 Zain 今年发布的这段视频突显了加沙灾难性的人道主义局势，以 10 岁难民汉达拉的标志性巴勒斯坦漫画为特色，传达了坚持和回归的信息</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 14:49:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-03-13/ty-article/.premium/the-viral-ramadan-commercial-spotlighting-palestinian-children-amid-israels-war-in-gaza/0000018e-3389-d9f7-a5ee-f7cbd44a0000</guid></item><item><titl